    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_012_058_000136",
    "sentence": "至午門外，皇帝衰服迎於午門內，舉哀，步導主升几筵殿。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_012_058_000137",
    "sentence": "皇帝立殿上，內侍請神主降輿升座，行安神禮。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_012_058_000138",
    "sentence": "皇帝四拜，興，奠酒，讀祝。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_012_058_000139",
    "sentence": "俯伏，興，四拜，舉哀。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_012_058_000140",
    "sentence": "皇太子以下陪拜。",
    "entities": [
