      {
        "text": "長陵",
        "label": "LOC"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_012_058_000188",
    "sentence": "吏部尚書蹇義等請祔廟後，素服御西角門視事。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "吏部尚書",
        "label": "TITLE"
      },
      {
        "text": "蹇義",
        "label": "PER"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_012_058_000189",
    "sentence": "至孟冬歲暮，行時饗禮。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_012_058_000190",
    "sentence": "鳴鐘鼓，黃袍御奉天門視朝。",
